    • Method Detail

      • getUserInfo

        UserInfo getUserInfo()
        Returns:
        UserInfo if user is already signed in, null otherwise.

      • observe

        rx.Observable<UserInfo> observe()
        UserInfo changes Observable.

        This is an infinite Observable - onComplete() and onError() will never be called.

        Note: This call will not perform any network requests.

        Returns:
        UserInfo observable.

      • isSignedIn

        boolean isSignedIn()
        Returns:
        true if user is signed in, false otherwise.
